  <h2>Why I'm Writing This</h2>
  
  <p>Three months ago, I watched a Wichita HVAC contractor spend 45 minutes on the phone trying to schedule one job.</p>
  
  <p>The homeowner called at 2 PM. The owner had to:</p>
